  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Setting the initial page loaded value can be achieved by:\r\n`<ais-hits-per-page :items=\"hitsPerPageOptions\" />`\r\nand\r\n```\r\ndata(){\r\nreturn {\r\nhitsPerPageOptions: [\r\n        { label: \"8 results\", value: 8, default: this.$router.currentRoute.query.hitsPerPage != 16 },\r\n        { label: \"16 results\", value: 16, default: this.$router.currentRoute.query.hitsPerPage == 16 }\r\n      ]\r\n}}\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2019-07-23T15:11:45Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5397#issuecomment-1367968931",
    "id": 1367968931,
